  "texts": [
    "Before reaching this phase, universities were more hesitant about adopting or banning the use of ChatGPT and other GenAI technologies.",
    "However, as time has progressed, opinions have begun to converge.",
    "In mid-April, HKU provided a free trial for staff to test ChatGPT, as well as announced that students \"may be able to use\" after the university has established related policies and guidelines.",
    "Coming up, HKUST and LU have also created their version of ChatGPT for staff and students to use.",
    "While universities have been providing GenAI software for both teachers and students to access, not all universities have released the software with detailed user guidelines covering necessary ethical and academic details."
  ],
